description: Bath & Body Works Brightest Bloom Scented Candle 411 g – a 3-wick candle with notes of fresh spring blossoms, soft petals, and a hint of warm musk. Made with premium fragrance oils and a clean-burning wax blend to create a cozy floral atmosphere.
direct_of_use:
1.	Trim wick to 1/4 inch before lighting.
	2.	Place candle on a heat-resistant surface, away from drafts and flammable objects.
	3.	Burn until the wax melts evenly across the surface, up to 3–4 hours at a time.
	4.	Extinguish with care and allow wax to cool before relighting.
